<p>I have a viewpager inside my recyclerview, viewpagers have 3 linearlayouts, I inflate them by using this example code </p>  <pre><code>@Override public Object instantiateItem(ViewGroup container, int position) {     View v = mLayoutInflater.inflate(R.layout.layout_one, container, false);     container.addView(v);     return v; } </code></pre>  <p>I have a custom view pager, on measure function is overridden,</p>  <pre><code>@Override protected void onMeasure(int widthMeasureSpec, int heightMeasureSpec) {     int height = 0;     for(int i = 0; i &lt; getChildCount(); i++) {         View child = getChildAt(i);         child.measure(widthMeasureSpec, MeasureSpec.makeMeasureSpec(0, MeasureSpec.UNSPECIFIED));         int h = child.getMeasuredHeight();         if(h &gt; height) height = h;     }     heightMeasureSpec = MeasureSpec.makeMeasureSpec(height, MeasureSpec.EXACTLY);     super.onMeasure(widthMeasureSpec, heightMeasureSpec); } </code></pre>  <p>My problem is, when I run this app all the linearlayouts are missing, </p>  <p>When I comment onMeasure function and add 300dp as height except wrap_content, I see linearlayout content</p>  <p>When I select a tab in tablayout, contents are shown also.</p>  <p>Hovewer, onMeasure is working when I add layout_one's content as xml inside viewpager, I am lost in this issue for two days, how can I solve this issue ?, thank you</p>